<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="idefd9d5c3-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="idefd9d5c4-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1991—Par. (22). <ref href="/us/pl/102/237">Pub. L. 102–237</ref> substituted “in-shell” for “inshell”.</p>
</note>
</notes>
